data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to live in one of Midtown Atlanta's prime condominium communities, 1010 Midtown. This spacious one bedroom unit with wrap around terraces and floor to ceiling windows offers exceptional city views. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, large granite island, and plenty of cabinets and pantry space. The fantastic open concept floor plan features a bright and airy living/ dining area and a lovely private bedroom with a beautiful ensuite bathroom. Amenities include state-of-the-art gym, luxe pool, outdoor grill area, resident lounge and front desk security / concierge. Walk Score of 94 - close to shopping, restaurants, coffee shops, Piedmont Park, The Beltline, High Museum, Colony Square, The Fox Theater and more! Don't miss this opportunity to live in wonderful Midtown Atlanta!
